  <h1>
    <span class="dark-green">More than just a host,</span> we're your offsite technical partner.
  </h1>
  <p>
    We provide long-term consulting and technical expertise for leading
    organizations. Our stability and one-on-one support is a result of the
    investments we’ve made into infrastructure, state of the art data
    centers and establishing an experienced team.
  </p>
  <p><a href="/hosting/about.html">Need more reasons to choose Gossamer?</a></p>
</div><!-- end .masthead -->

<div class="span-24 bg-rule-12col clearfix">
  <div class="span-11 append-1 content-text"><!-- left-col-->
    <p><img src="http://static.gossamer-threads.com/r3/images/hosting/engineers2.jpg" width="430" height="216" alt="Engineers" /></p>

    <h2>Direct access to the engineers</h2>
    <p>
      We provide immediate access to our experienced support team, 24/7. Our
      team of web engineers design and develop the entire platforms on which
      our clients’ sites reside, so they know the infrastructure
      intimately.
    </p>
    <p><img src="http://static.gossamer-threads.com/r3/images/hosting/technology2.jpg" width="430" height="216" alt="Technology" /></p>

    <h2>Deep roots in technology</h2>
    <p>
      We’ve been developing applications for over 18 years. In
      fact, we first made our name as application developers. Given our
      extensive experience with the hardware and software behind the websites
      we host, we’re able to troubleshoot, offer customized solutions, and
      implement changes quickly and efficiently.
    </p>
    <p><img src="http://static.gossamer-threads.com/r3/images/hosting/data-center2.jpg" width="430" height="216" alt="Data center/hosting" /></p>

    <h2>A long-term approach</h2>
    <p>
      A number of large organizations have turned to Gossamer Threads for
      secure, reliable hosting of their high availability websites. While some
      initially come to us for one-off projects, many eventually partner with
      us long-term. This allows us to get to know their big picture needs, and
      in turn, build web solutions around those needs.
    </p>
  </div><!-- end left-col-->

